  ],
  "subject": [],
  "abstracts": [
    {
      "note": "",
      "abstract": "Requires the state interagency coordinating council for services to persons who are deaf, deaf-blind, or hard of hearing to develop and implement a training program to educate first responders on effective communication with deaf and hard of hearing individuals in emergency situations."
    }
